# User story title: Sign up as a customer

Keep any other version here as well, e.g. Create account for service booking.

## Priority: 1
High priority for iteration-1. Needed to allow customer participation.

## Estimation: 2 days
* Bob: 2 days
* Lisa: 1.5 days
* Jack: 2 days

## Assumptions:
* Users will provide email, password, phone number, address, and payment info.
* Users are not applying as artists.

## Description:
Description-v1: As a customer, I want to create an account by providing my personal details and payment information, so I can use the services offered.

## Tasks:
1. Create a registration form for customers, Estimation: 0.5 days
2. Add input validation for form fields, Estimation: 0.5 days
3. Save customer info to database, Estimation: 1 day
4. Display success message and redirect, Estimation: 0.5 day

